videos.description: Rocket Watts knocks down the corner 3-pointer giving the Spartans the early 9-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Watts' 3 gives MSU the early 9-0 lead) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Watts' 3 gives MSU the early 9-0 lead

videos.description: Jalen Smith corrals the pass and throws the perfect kick out to Donta Scott for the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Smith throws the running pass to Scott for the 3) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Smith throws the running pass to Scott for the 3

videos.description: Cassius Winston steps into the 3-pointer and drains it from the top of the key.
videos.headline: Winston knocks down 3-pointer

videos.description: Jalen Smith denies Xavier Tillman Sr. by blocking his shot with his elbow.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Smith blocks Tillman with his elbow) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Smith blocks Tillman with his elbow

videos.description: Cassius Winston drains a half-court shot right as the buzzer goes off to end the first half.
videos.headline: Winston drains half-court shot

videos.description: Xavier Tillman Sr. plays great defense on Jalen Smith then beats his man down the court for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tillman plays defense, then gets layup) 2020/02/29

videos.headline: Tillman plays defense, then gets layup

videos.description: Jalen Smith spins off the defender and gets the and-1 to go.
videos.headline: Smith gets impressive and-1

videos.description: Jalen Smith and Marcus Bingham Jr. have to be separated after battling for a rebound, and both receive technical.
